messages.messageBody:
I have been looking. I thought that I found jackpot the other day. $35,000
for a house on 20+ acres. The house would have been perfect for us, but there
was the typo of the acreage. There are ZERO acres. LOL Oh well, I keep
looking.

Blessings,
Stephanie
Teacher and Mommy of 4 homeschooling fanatics, wife to the best principal,
protector of many pets and wild ones, and unpublished writer.
***Life's Learnings Academy - Protecting Our Children***
